__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

** it will keep scrolling until there is no room for srolling 


//smooth scrolling with Interval

_________________________________________________________________


____________________________

var scollInerval=setInterval(function(){
    window.scrollBy(0,50);                 //50px down in each interval
},500);                                    //each scroll has an interval of 500 mili second

____________________________


**when you will try to sroll up , it will drag you down,
  why??
  --because we have started an interval

_________________________________________________________________
   so to stop scrolling down
           we use 
             |
             |
             V
   clearInterval(nameOfTheIntervalVariable);
   i.e., clearInterval(scollInerval);
             |
             |
             V
             
___________________________

var scollInerval=setInterval(function(){
    window.scrollBy(0,50);                 
},500); 


clearInterval(scollInerval);
